                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote scope="major" script="nastaliq" medium="ink">
                        <p>Written in nasta‘liq script in <material>black ink</material> with names, sub-headers, and corrections in red.</p></handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="shikasta" medium="ink">
                        <p>Marginalia and emendations to the text in a second shikasta-ta‘liq hand in <material>black ink</material>.</p>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
